{"tid":96752,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【三點九沈大師】大師：兩個做法 2017-1-27 12:12:35","createTime":"2017-01-27T06:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T07:59:55.000Z","uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aece2ed98b68cc3eef84aaea178d3652db3fa756","tid":96752,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:03:10.000Z","msg":"【三點九沈大師】大師：兩個做法<br />\n2017-1-27 12:12:35<br />\n<br />\n【三點九沈大師】大師：兩個做法 <br />\n<br />\n今日變咗《十一點九沈大師》時間，個市你見喇牛牛皮皮，預咗咁㗎喇，放完假返o黎個市有機會抽一抽高先嘅，但預算上面空間未必太大，跟住會有回吐，所以兩個做法啦，價外Call/Put輪兩邊做博佢漲引伸波幅，兼可能開高完穿返落去，射兩邊，另一個做法就等假期返o黎之後開高先至沽佢，仍然都係嗰個策略，要Call嘅Call滙豐（<a href=\"http://00005.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00005.HK&d=bdENBHZHXM2N6cv0Qg04S3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a7cec311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00005.HK</a>），要沽嘅沽港交所（<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=bdENBHZHXM2N6cv0Qg04S3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=080c51d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>），呢兩個Pair Trade（配對交易）o黎做都可以。"},{"pid":"130e1261180a6fb6976cfcf8ce56e69ff9746ea0","tid":96752,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:04:01.000Z","msg":"師父有兩碌鳩咩？<br />\n射兩邊<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6SLxQU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6SLxQU.gif&h=af33764f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6E4Z8s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6E4Z8s.gif&h=8c860226&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W2zNaL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW2zNaL.gif&h=2756cc01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5b3a08ef0f18892b8651772558f6d4d38a02456d","tid":96752,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"個頭盔由頭笠到落腳，冚家剷點都有位比師父彈出彈入，參透實戰理論一啲都唔簡單 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f379ecb66578b3927